WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.177
Creating a proposal is quick.

00:00:02.177 --> 00:00:07.658
You open “New proposal”, pick the client and add lines from the catalogue

00:00:07.658 --> 00:00:11.637
the description, price and VAT fill in by themselves.

00:00:11.637 --> 00:00:17.043
The totals, with discount and regional VAT, are calculated in real time.

00:00:17.043 --> 00:00:19.370
Then you just preview and save.
